nodes.text: Cliff Chiang is an American[source?] comic book artist. He created several illustrations for the 2010 trading card series 2010 Topps Star Wars Galaxy Series 5, and these illustrations later appeared in the 2016 reference book Star Wars Propaganda: A History of Persuasive Art in the Galaxy. He also created one of the variant covers for the 2016 comic Darth Vader 25.
